Title: Ex Deus Machina
Plot: SG-1 investigates when evidence suggests that there are still Goa'uld hiding on Earth -- including a former System Lord. Tensions between Earth and the Free Jaffa continue to mount.
GuestStars: Cliff Simon, Kendall Cross, Barclay Hope, Gary Jones, Louis Gossett Jr., Gardiner Millar, Simone Bailly, Kevin Blatch
